  "sections": [
    {
      "name": "Fleshwarp Amalgam",
      "sources": [
        {
          "link": {
            "alt": "Battlecry! pg. 180",
            "aonid": 268,
            "game-obj": "Sources",
            "name": "Battlecry! pg. 180",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "Battlecry!",
          "page": 180,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "While fleshwarpers would like every creation to be perfect, they produce countless rejects. Many of these are killed at creation. But some still have some use, turning imperfection into some kind of weapon. These rejects\u2014 mounds of flesh, carapaces, and too many limbs\u2014can be whipped into a frenzy and set against enemy forces.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
