          "effect": "The fleshwarp amalgam lashes out in retaliation. Each enemy in a 5-foot emanation takes 2d10+6 bludgeoning or slashing damage (DC 23 basic Reflex). A creature who fails the save is also pushed 5 feet away from the amalgam.",
