            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The fleshwarp amalgam sprays acid from their various orifices, combining the streams into a powerful spray. This acid spray is a 10-foot burst that deals 3d8 acid damage (DC 23 basic Reflex save) within 60 feet. A creature who critically fails their saving throw takes 1d8 persistent acid damage. When the troop is reduced to 2 segments, this area decreases to a 5-foot burst.",
            "traits": [
              {
                "alternate_link": {
                  "alternate_type": "legacy",
